metadata.description:
Baros played in several countries. In England he also did it at Aston Villa and Portsmouth, while in Turkey he wore the colors of Galatasaray and Antalyaspor. He won the Champions League with Liverpool in 2005 and retired from the Czech Republic team after Euro 2012.

Your own as a custom playable Metaverse Avatar is arriving. Play to earn games are gonna be launched in partnership with Studio 54 and the integration as playable avatars into the game is now in development.
